ze: 2.25rem;\n      font-weight: 600;\n      line-height: 1.25;\n      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;\n    }\n\n    .effective-date {\n      color: var(--text-secondary);\n      font-size: 0.9rem;\n      margin-bottom: 2.5rem;\n      padding-bottom: 2rem;\n      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);\n    }\n\n    .intro {\n      font-size: 1.05rem;\n      color: var(--text-secondary);\n      margin-bottom: 2.5rem;\n      line-height: 1.8;\n    }\n\n    h2 {\n      font-family: 'Source Serif 4', Georgia, serif;\n      font-size: 1.4rem;\n      font-weight: 600;\n      margin-top: 2.75rem;\n      margin-bottom: 1rem;\n      color: var(--text);\n    }\n\n    p {\n      margin-bottom: 1rem;\n    }\n\n    ul {\n      margin: 0.75rem 0 1.25rem 1.5rem;\n    }\n\n    li {\n      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;\n      line-height: 1.7;\n    }\n\n    .highlight-box {\n      background: var(--accent-light);\n      border-left: 3px solid var(--accent);\n      padding: 1rem 1.25rem;\n      border-radius: 0 var(--radius) var(--radius) 0;\n      margin: 1.25rem 0;\n      font-size: 0.95rem;\n    }\n\n    .contact-section {\n      background: var(--surface);\n      border: 1px solid var(--border);\n      border-radius: var(--radius);\n      padding: 1.5rem;\n      margin-top: 2rem;\n    }\n\n    .contact-section a {\n      color: var(--accent);\n      text-decoration: none;\n    }\n\n    .contact-section a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }\n\n    .footer {\n      max-width: 800px;\n      margin: 0 auto;\n      padding: 2rem;\n      border-top: 1px solid var(--border);\n      text-align: center;\n      font-size: 0.85rem;\n      color: var(--text-secondary);\n    }\n\n    @media (max-width: 640px) {\n      main { padding: 2rem 1.25rem 3rem; }\n      .page-title { font-size: 1.75rem; }\n      h2 { font-size: 1.2rem; }\n      .header { padding: 1rem 1.25rem; }\n    }\n  </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n  <header class=\"header\">\n    <div class=\"header-inner\">\n      <a href=\"/\" class=\"logo\">VelzenLabs</a>\n      <a href=\"/\" class=\"back-link\">&larr; Back to Home</a>\n    </div>\n  </header>\n\n  <main>\n    <h1 class=\"page-title\">Privacy Policy</h1>\n    <p class=\"effective-date\">Effective Date: July 13, 2026</p>\n\n    <p class=\"intro\">\n      VelzenLabs, a sole proprietorship based in Chennai, India (\"we\", \"our\", or \"us\") respects your privacy and is committed to protecting the personal information you share with us. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, disclose, and protect information when you use our website, AI automation services, and integrations with third-party platforms including Meta (Facebook, Instagram, and WhatsApp).\n    </p>\n\n    <p>By using our services, you agree to this Privacy Policy.</p>\n\n    <h2>Information We Collect</h2>\n    <p>Depending on the services you use, we may collect:</p>\n    <ul>\n      <li>Name and contact information</li>\n      <li>Email address</li>\n      <li>Business information</li>\n      <li>Instagram Business Account information</li>\n      <li>Facebook Page information</li>\n      <li>WhatsApp Business information</li>\n      <li>Public profile information authorized through Meta Login</li>\n      <li>Messages exchanged with AI assistants or chatbots</li>\n      <li>Technical information such as IP address, browser type, device information, and usage logs</li>\n    </ul>\n    <p>We only collect information necessary to provide our services.</p>\n\n    <h2>How We Use Your Information</h2>\n    <p>We use your information to:</p>\n    <ul>\n      <li>Provide AI-powered automation services</li>\n      <li>Respond to customer inquiries</li>\n      <li>Automate customer communication</li>\n      <li>Improve our products and services</li>\n      <li>Maintain system security</li>\n      <li>Prevent fraud and misuse</li>\n      <li>Comply with legal obligations</li>\n      <li>Integrate with Meta APIs as authorized by users</li>\n    </ul>\n\n    <h2>Meta Platform Data</h2>\n    <p>If you authorize VelzenLabs to access your Meta accounts, we may access information permitted by the permissions you grant, including:</p>\n    <ul>\n      <li>Instagram Business Account information</li>\n      <li>Facebook Page information</li>\n      <li>Messages</li>\n      <li>User identifiers required for API functionality</li>\n    </ul>\n    <div class=\"highlight-box\">\n      We do not use Meta data for advertising or sell it to third parties.\n    </div>\n\n    <h2>Data Sharing</h2>\n    <p>We do not sell your personal information.</p>\n    <p>Information may be shared only with:</p>\n    <ul>\n      <li>Cloud infrastructure providers</li>\n      <li>AI service providers required to process requests</li>\n      <li>Payment providers (when applicable)</li>\n      <li>Government authorities if required by law</li>\n    </ul>\n\n    <h2>Data Security</h2>\n    <p>We implement appropriate administrative, technical, and organizational safeguards to protect your information against unauthorized access, alteration, disclosure, or destruction.</p>\n\n    <h2>Data Retention</h2>\n    <p>We retain information only as long as necessary to provide our services, comply with legal obligations, resolve disputes, and enforce our agreements.</p>\n\n    <h2>Your Rights</h2>\n    <p>Depending on your location, you may have the right to:</p>\n    <ul>\n      <li>Access your personal information</li>\n      <li>Correct inaccurate information</li>\n      <li>Request deletion of your data</li>\n      <li>Withdraw permissions granted through Meta</li>\n      <li>Object to or restrict certain processing of your data</li>\n      <li>Request information about how your data is processed</li>\n    </ul>\n    <p>To exercise any of these rights, email us at <a href=\"mailto:privacy@velzenlabs.com\" style=\"color:var(--accent)\">privacy@velzenlabs.com</a>. We will respond to your request within 30 days.</p>\n\n    <h2>Meta Platform Data Deletion &amp; Deauthorization</h2>\n    <p>When you disconnect VelzenLabs from your Meta account or revoke permissions, we will delete all Meta Platform Data associated with your account within 30 days. You can also request data deletion at any time by emailing us.</p>\n    <p>For more details, visit our <a href=\"/data-deletion.html\" style=\"color:var(--accent)\">Data Deletion Instructions</a> page.</p>\n\n    <h2>Children's Privacy</h2>\n    <p>Our services are intended for businesses and individuals aged 18 and above. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children under 13 (or under 16 in the European Economic Area). If we become aware that we have collected data from a child, we will take steps to delete it promptly. If you believe a child has provided us with personal information, please contact us immediately.</p>\n\n    <h2>Cookies &amp; Tracking Technologies</h2>\n    <p>Our website may use cookies and similar tracking technologies to improve your experience, analyze usage patterns, and maintain system security. These may include essential cookies required for the website to function and analytics cookies that help us understand how visitors interact with our site. You can control cookie preferences through your browser settings.</p>\n\n    <h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>\n    <p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. When we make material changes, we will notify you by updating the effective date at the top of this page and, where possible, by sending a notification to the email address associated with your account. Your continued use of our services after such changes constitutes acceptance of the updated policy.</p>\n\n    <h2>Contact Us</h2>\n    <div class=\"contact-section\">\n      <p>If you have questions about this Privacy Policy or wish to exercise your rights, please contact us at:</p>\n      <p><strong>VelzenLabs</strong></p>\n      <p>Chennai, Tamil Nadu, India</p>\n      <p>Email: <a href=\"mailto:privacy@velzenlabs.com\">privacy@velzenlabs.com</a></p>\n    </div>\n  </main>\n\n  <footer class=\"footer\">\n    &copy; 2026 VelzenLabs. All rights reserved.\n  </footer>\n\n</body>\n</html>\n",
