ar(--text-secondary); margin-bottom: 2.5rem; line-height: 1.8; }\n    h2 { font-family: 'Source Serif 4', Georgia, serif; font-size: 1.4rem; font-weight: 600; margin-top: 2.75rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: var(--text); }\n    p { margin-bottom: 1rem; }\n    ul { margin: 0.75rem 0 1.25rem 1.5rem; }\n    li { margin-bottom: 0.5rem; line-height: 1.7; }\n    .highlight-box { background: var(--accent-light); border-left: 3px solid var(--accent); padding: 1rem 1.25rem; border-radius: 0 var(--radius) var(--radius) 0; margin: 1.25rem 0; font-size: 0.95rem; }\n    .contact-section { background: var(--surface); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: var(--radius); padding: 1.5rem; margin-top: 2rem; }\n    .contact-section a { color: var(--accent); text-decoration: none; }\n    .contact-section a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }\n    a { color: var(--accent); text-decoration: none; }\n    a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }\n    .footer { max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 2rem; border-top: 1px solid var(--border); text-align: center; font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--text-secondary); }\n    @media (max-width: 640px) {\n      main { padding: 2rem 1.25rem 3rem; }\n      .page-title { font-size: 1.75rem; }\n      h2 { font-size: 1.2rem; }\n      .header { padding: 1rem 1.25rem; }\n    }\n  </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n  <header class=\"header\">\n    <div class=\"header-inner\">\n      <a href=\"/\" class=\"logo\">VelzenLabs</a>\n      <a href=\"/\" class=\"back-link\">&larr; Back to Home</a>\n    </div>\n  </header>\n\n  <main>\n    <h1 class=\"page-title\">Terms of Service</h1>\n    <p class=\"effective-date\">Effective Date: July 13, 2026</p>\n\n    <p class=\"intro\">\n      These Terms of Service (\"Terms\") govern your access to and use of the services provided by VelzenLabs, a sole proprietorship based in Chennai, India (\"we\", \"our\", or \"us\"). By accessing or using our services, you agree to be bound by these Terms.\n    </p>\n\n    <h2>1. Services</h2>\n    <p>VelzenLabs provides AI-powered automation services, including chatbot development, messaging automation, and integrations with third-party platforms such as Meta (Facebook, Instagram, and WhatsApp). The specific features and scope of services may vary and are subject to change.</p>\n\n    <h2>2. Eligibility</h2>\n    <p>You must be at least 18 years of age and have the legal authority to enter into these Terms. If you are using our services on behalf of a business, you represent that you have the authority to bind that business to these Terms.</p>\n\n    <h2>3. Your Account</h2>\n    <p>You are responsible for maintaining the confidentiality of any account credentials associated with your use of our services. You agree to notify us immediately of any unauthorized use of your account. We are not liable for any loss resulting from unauthorized access to your account.</p>\n\n    <h2>4. Acceptable Use</h2>\n    <p>When using our services, you agree not to:</p>\n    <ul>\n      <li>Violate any applicable laws or regulations</li>\n      <li>Infringe the rights of any third party</li>\n      <li>Send spam, unsolicited messages, or bulk communications through our AI tools</li>\n      <li>Use our services to harass, threaten, or harm others</li>\n      <li>Attempt to gain unauthorized access to our systems or networks</li>\n      <li>Use our services in any way that violates Meta's Platform Terms or Developer Policies</li>\n      <li>Reverse-engineer, decompile, or disassemble any part of our services</li>\n    </ul>\n\n    <h2>5. Third-Party Platforms</h2>\n    <p>Our services integrate with third-party platforms, including Meta (Facebook, Instagram, and WhatsApp). Your use of these platforms is subject to their respective terms and policies. We are not responsible for the availability, accuracy, or practices of any third-party platform. When you connect your Meta account, you authorize us to access and use data in accordance with the permissions you grant and our <a href=\"/privacy-policy.html\">Privacy Policy</a>.</p>\n\n    <h2>6. Intellectual Property</h2>\n    <p>All content, software, technology, and materials provided through our services are the property of VelzenLabs or our licensors and are protected by applicable intellectual property laws. You may not copy, modify, distribute, or create derivative works from our services without our prior written consent.</p>\n    <p>You retain ownership of any content you provide to us. By using our services, you grant us a limited, non-exclusive license to use your content solely for the purpose of providing and improving our services.</p>\n\n    <h2>7. AI-Generated Content</h2>\n    <p>Our services may generate automated responses and content using artificial intelligence. While we strive for accuracy, AI-generated content may not always be correct, complete, or suitable for your specific needs. You are responsible for reviewing and verifying any AI-generated content before relying on it.</p>\n\n    <h2>8. Limitation of Liability</h2>\n    <p>To the maximum extent permitted by applicable law, VelzenLabs shall not be liable for any indirect, incidental, special, consequential, or punitive damages, or any loss of profits, revenue, data, or business opportunities arising out of or related to your use of our services.</p>\n    <p>Our total liability for any claim arising out of these Terms shall not exceed the amount you paid us in the twelve months preceding the claim.</p>\n\n    <h2>9. Disclaimer of Warranties</h2>\n    <p>Our services are provided on an \"as is\" and \"as available\" basis without warranties of any kind, whether express, implied, or statutory, including warranties of merchantability, fitness for a particular purpose, and non-infringement.</p>\n\n    <h2>10. Termination</h2>\n    <p>Either party may terminate this agreement at any time. We may suspend or terminate your access to our services if you violate these Terms or if required by law. Upon termination, your right to use our services will cease immediately. Provisions that by their nature should survive termination will continue to apply.</p>\n\n    <h2>11. Changes to These Terms</h2>\n    <p>We may update these Terms from time to time. When we make material changes, we will update the effective date at the top of this page and notify you where possible. Your continued use of our services after changes are posted constitutes acceptance of the updated Terms.</p>\n\n    <h2>12. Governing Law</h2>\n    <p>These Terms are governed by and construed in accordance with the laws of India. Any disputes arising out of these Terms shall be subject to the exclusive jurisdiction of the courts in Chennai, Tamil Nadu, India.</p>\n\n    <h2>13. Contact Us</h2>\n    <div class=\"contact-section\">\n      <p>If you have questions about these Terms, please contact us at:</p>\n      <p><strong>VelzenLabs</strong></p>\n      <p>Chennai, Tamil Nadu, India</p>\n      <p>Email: <a href=\"mailto:contact@velzenlabs.com\">contact@velzenlabs.com</a></p>\n    </div>\n  </main>\n\n  <footer class=\"footer\">\n    &copy; 2026 VelzenLabs. All rights reserved. |\n    <a href=\"/privacy-policy.html\">Privacy Policy</a> |\n    <a href=\"/data-deletion.html\">Data Deletion</a>\n  </footer>\n\n</body>\n</html>\n",
  "data-deletion": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n  <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n  <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n  <title>Data Deletion Instructions \u2014 VelzenLabs</title>\n  <meta name=\"description\" content=\"How to request deletion of your data from VelzenLabs.\">\n  <link rel=\"preconnect\" href=\"https://fonts.googleapis.com\">\n  <link href=\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600&family=Source+Serif+4:opsz,wght@8..60,400;8..60,600&display=swap\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n  <style>\n    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }\n    :root {\n      --bg: #FAFAFA; --surface: #FFFFFF; --text: #1A1A1A;\n      --text-secondary: #555; --accent: #2A5BD7; --accent-light: #EBF0FC;\n      --border: #E2E2E2; --radius: 8px;\n    }\n    body { font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif; background: var(--bg); color: var(--text); line-height: 1.7; font-size: 16px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; }\n    .header { background: var(--surface); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); padding: 1.25rem 2rem; }\n    .header-inner { max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; }\n    .logo { font-family: 'Source Serif 4', Georgia, serif; font-weight: 600; font-size: 1.25rem; color: var(--text); text-decoration: none; }\n    .back-link { font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--accent); text-decoration: none; }\n    .back-link:hover { text-decoration: underline; }\n    main { max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 3rem 2rem 5rem; }\n    .page-title { font-family: 'Source Serif 4', Georgia, serif; font-size: 2.25rem; font-weight: 600; line-height: 1.25; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }\n    .effective-date { color: var(--text-secondary); font-size: 0.9rem; margin-bottom: 2.5rem; padding-bottom: 2rem; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); }\n    .intro { font-size: 1.05rem; color: var(--text-secondary); margin-bottom: 2.5rem; line-height: 1.8; }\n    h2 { font-family: 'Source Serif 4', Georgia, serif; font-size: 1.4rem; font-weight: 600; margin-top: 2.75rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: var(--text); }\n    p { margin-bottom: 1rem; }\n    a { color: var(--accent); text-decoration: none; }\n    a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }\n\n    .steps { counter-reset: steps; margin: 1.5rem 0; }\n    .step {\n      counter-increment: steps;\n      display: flex;\n      gap: 1rem;\n      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;\n      align-items: flex-start;\n    }\n    .step-number {\n      flex-shrink: 0;\n      width: 36px; height: 36px;\n      background: var(--accent);\n      color: #fff;\n      border-radius: 50%;\n      display: flex;\n      align-items: center;\n      justify-content: center;\n      font-weight: 600;\n      font-size: 0.9rem;\n    }\n    .step-content { padding-top: 0.35rem; }\n    .step-content strong { display: block; margin-bottom: 0.25rem; }\n\n    .highlight-box {\n      background: var(--accent-light);\n      border-left: 3px solid var(--accent);\n      padding: 1rem 1.25rem;\n      border-radius: 0 var(--radius) var(--radius) 0;\n      margin: 1.5rem 0;\n      font-size: 0.95rem;\n    }\n\n    .contact-section {\n      background: var(--surface);\n      border: 1px solid var(--border);\n      border-radius: var(--radius);\n      padding: 1.5rem;\n      margin-top: 2rem;\n    }\n\n    .footer { max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 2rem; border-top: 1px solid var(--border); text-align: center; font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--text-secondary); }\n\n    @media (max-width: 640px) {\n      main { padding: 2rem 1.25rem 3rem; }\n      .page-title { font-size: 1.75rem; }\n      h2 { font-size: 1.2rem; }\n      .header { padding: 1rem 1.25rem; }\n    }\n  </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n  <header class=\"header\">\n    <div class=\"header-inner\">\n      <a href=\"/\" class=\"logo\">VelzenLabs</a>\n      <a href=\"/\" class=\"back-link\">&larr; Back to Home</a>\n    </div>\n  </header>\n\n  <main>\n    <h1 class=\"page-title\">Data Deletion Instructions</h1>\n    <p class=\"effective-date\">Effective Date: July 13, 2026</p>\n\n    <p class=\"intro\">\n      VelzenLabs respects your right to control your personal data. If you want to delete the data we have collected through your use of our services or your Meta (Facebook, Instagram, WhatsApp) integration, you can follow the steps below.\n    </p>\n\n    <h2>How to Request Data Deletion</h2>\n\n    <div class=\"steps\">\n      <div class=\"step\">\n        <div class=\"step-number\">1</div>\n        <div class=\"step-content\">\n          <strong>Send us an email</strong>\n          Email <a href=\"mailto:privacy@velzenlabs.com\">privacy@velzenlabs.com</a> with the subject line \"Data Deletion Request\". Include your name and the email address or Meta account associated with our services.\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"step\">\n        <div class=\"step-number\">2</div>\n        <div class=\"step-content\">\n          <strong>We verify your identity</strong>\n          To protect your privacy, we may ask you to verify your identity before processing your request. This helps ensure that no one else can delete your data on your behalf.\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"step\">\n        <div class=\"step-number\">3</div>\n        <div class=\"step-content\">\n          <strong>We process your request</strong>\n          Once verified, we will delete your personal data from our systems within 30 days. You will receive a confirmation email when the deletion is complete.\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <h2>Removing Meta Permissions</h2>\n    <p>You can also revoke VelzenLabs' access to your Meta data directly from your Meta account:</p>\n\n    <div class=\"steps\">\n      <div class=\"step\">\n        <div class=\"step-number\">1</div>\n        <div class=\"step-content\">\n          <strong>Facebook</strong>\n          Go to <strong>Settings &amp; Privacy &rarr; Settings &rarr; Apps and Websites</strong>, find VelzenLabs, and click <strong>Remove</strong>.\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"step\">\n        <div class=\"step-number\">2</div>\n        <div class=\"step-content\">\n          <strong>Instagram</strong>\n          Go to <strong>Settings &rarr; Security &rarr; Apps and Websites</strong>, find VelzenLabs, and click <strong>Remove</strong>.\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"highlight-box\">\n      When you revoke our access through Meta or request deletion through email, we will delete all Meta Platform Data associated with your account from our systems within 30 days. Some data may be retained if required by law.\n    </div>\n\n    <h2>What Data Gets Deleted</h2>\n    <p>Upon a valid deletion request, we will delete:</p>\n    <ul style=\"margin: 0.75rem 0 1.25rem 1.5rem;\">\n      <li>Your personal information (name, email, contact details)</li>\n      <li>Meta account data (Facebook Page, Instagram, WhatsApp information)</li>\n      <li>Messages and conversation logs processed by our AI services</li>\n      <li>Usage logs and technical data linked to your account</li>\n    </ul>\n    <p>Data that has been anonymized or aggregated in a way that can no longer identify you may be retained for analytics and service improvement purposes.</p>\n\n    <h2>Contact Us</h2>\n    <div class=\"contact-section\">\n      <p>For data deletion requests or any questions about your data, please contact us at:</p>\n      <p><strong>VelzenLabs</strong></p>\n      <p>Chennai, Tamil Nadu, India</p>\n      <p>Email: <a href=\"mailto:privacy@velzenlabs.com\">privacy@velzenlabs.com</a></p>\n    </div>\n  </main>\n\n  <footer class=\"footer\">\n    &copy; 2026 VelzenLabs. All rights reserved. |\n    <a href=\"/privacy-policy.html\">Privacy Policy</a> |\n    <a href=\"/terms-of-service.html\">Terms of Service</a>\n  </footer>\n\n</body>\n</html>\n"
};

module.exports = (req, res) => {
  const page = (req.query && req.query.page) || 'privacy-policy';
  const html = PAGES[page] || PAGES['privacy-policy'];

  res.statusCode = 200;
  res.setHeader('Content-Type', 'text/html; charset=utf-8');
  res.setHeader('Cache-Control', 'public, max-age=0, must-revalidate');
  res.end(html);
};
